<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFE8FFABFF152FDDFF58F931" bold="true" box="[136,241,1736,1762]" pageId="1" pageNumber="248">Notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFE8FFABFF6D2FDDFE7BF931" authorityName="Cogniaux" authorityYear="1885" box="[240,466,1736,1762]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="amazonica">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFE8FFABFF6D2FDDFE7BF931" box="[240,466,1736,1762]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="248">Comolia amazonica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was considered a synonym for 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFE8FFABFCA62FDDFB3EF931" authority="(Aubl.) Triana" authorityName="Triana" authorityYear="1871" baseAuthorityName="Aubl." box="[827,1175,1736,1763]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Comolia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="villosa">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFE8FFABFCA62FDDFC47F931" box="[827,1006,1736,1762]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="248">Comolia villosa</emphasis>
(Aubl.) Triana
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFE8FFABFB592FDDFAE6F930" author="Seco, R. C." box="[1220,1359,1736,1763]" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" refId="ref10541" refString="Seco, R. C. (2006) Estudos taxonomicos no genero Comolia DC. (Melastomataceae - Melastomeae) no Brasil. Instituto de Biologia, Universidade Estadual de Campinas, Campinas, 113 pp." type="book" year="2006">Seco (2006)</bibRefCitation>
, but not by 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFE8FFABFF332FF9FE3AF8D5" author="Rocha, M. J. R. &amp; Guimaraes, P. J. F. &amp; Michelangeli, F. A. &amp; Batista, J. A. N." box="[174,403,1772,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" pagination="50 - 74" refId="ref10431" refString="Rocha, M. J. R., Guimaraes, P. J. F., Michelangeli, F. A. &amp; Batista, J. A. N. (2018) Taxonomy of Marcetieae: A new neotropical tribe of Melastomataceae. International Journal of Plant Sciences 179: 50 - 74. https: // doi. org / 10.1086 / 694932" type="journal article" year="2018">
Rocha 
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFE8FFABFE9D2FF8FE9DF8D5" box="[256,308,1772,1798]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="248">et al</emphasis>
. (2018)
</bibRefCitation>
. When describing this species, 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFE8FFABFC9D2FF9FC6BF8D4" author="Cogniaux, A." box="[768,962,1772,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" refId="ref8702" refString="Cogniaux, A. (1885) Melastomaceae. Tribus II. Tibouchineae Baill. In: Martius, C. F. P. &amp; Eichler, A. G. (Eds.) Flora brasiliensis, enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum: quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas. Vol. 14. Frid. Fleischer, Monachii et Lipsiae [Munich &amp; Leipzig], pp. 205 - 510. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 454" type="book" year="1885">Cogniaux (1885)</bibRefCitation>
indicated 
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFE8FFABFBA02FF8FABAF8D5" box="[1085,1299,1772,1798]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="248">
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFE8FFABFBA02FF8FBF9F8D5" box="[1085,1104,1773,1798]" country="United Kingdom" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15670" name="Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" type="Herbarium">E</collectionCode>
. 
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFE8FFABFBCE2FF8FBCFF8D5" box="[1107,1126,1773,1798]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15707" name="Field Museum of Natural History, Botany Department" pageId="1" pageNumber="248" type="Herbarium">F</collectionCode>
. Poeppig 2996
</emphasis>
as examined and reported that there are duplicates deposited at “ 
